member.remarks:
This is useful for creating examples or unit tests. Press Ctrl+Alt+C in a plot to copy code to the clipboard.
            Usage:

            var cg = new CodeGenerator(myPlotModel);
            Clipboard.SetText(cg.ToCode());

member.example:
Subscript: H_{2}O
            Superscript: E=mc^{2}
            Both: A^{2}_{i,j}

